'''Keff Base''' was a [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel]] base in the [[Sullust system/Legends|Sullust system]]. It was on this base that the [[Alliance High Command/Legends|Alliance High Command]] received the [[Death Star II/Legends|Death Star II]] plans from the [[Deep Ear]] faction of the [[Bothan Spynet/Legends|Bothan Spynet]].

